 [X]  RFC 7986 - New iCalendar Properties
  COLOR:#FF5733          # Calendar item colors
  CONFERENCE:https://...  # Video call links (Zoom, Meet, Teams)
  IMAGE:https://...       # Event images/logos
  Modern calendar clients use these. Low effort, high value.

 [X] Managed Attachments (RFC 8607) Instead of inline base64 attachments, store them server-side with URLs. Better for large files and bandwidth.

